Theſe be ſpeciall times: the generall ſhould haue beene firſt noted, viz. When Gods children haue gotten ſome ſtocke and ſtrength; for the Lord is wiſe, and will not vſe an Iron Inſtrument to threſh out Cummin; 
                  Eſay. 28. hee will not lay weight vpon greene Timber, but firſt ſeaſon it, and then employ it after. 
                  Ioh. 21. Thus while Peter was young hee walked at large, but after was diſtreſſed. Thus for the When.
